SUMMARY:Part Closure: WINDRUSH LINE: Saturday 7 and Sunday 8 March 
 (Including Friday and Saturday Night Overground)\, no service between 
 Highbury & Islington and New Cross Gate / New Cross / Clapham Junction / 
 Battersea Park. During Night Overground hours\, please use local London 
 Buses services. Use MILDMAY LINE services on Saturday between Highbury & 
 Islington\, Canonbury and Dalston Kingsland. On Saturday only\, between 
 0700 and 2200\, a special train service operates between London Bridge and
  West Croydon calling at New Cross Gate and all stations (change at 
 Sydenham for SOUTHERN services to/from Crystal Palace). On Saturday only\,
  SOUTHERN services continue to serve Queens Road Peckham and Peckham Rye\,
  on Sunday\, a further replacement bus service operates between London 
 Bridge and Streatham via these stations. On Sunday\, trains operate 
 between New Cross Gate and West Croydon / Crystal Palace only. Replacement
  bus services also operate during the day.
END:VEVENT
